<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="/">TheCubeCollective</a>
      <div class="welcome-banner" id="welcome-banner"></div>
    </div>
    <nav class="main-nav">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#welcome">Welcome</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li><a href="#servers">Servers</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li><a href="#community">Community</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li><a href="#discord">Discord</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="content">
    <section id="welcome" class="welcome-section">
      <div class="side-title">Welcome</div>
      <div class="section-content highlight">
        <h2>Welcome to TheCubeCollective</h2>
        <p>Welcome to TheCubeCollective, a diverse and passionate gaming community where players from around the globe come together to enjoy Minecraft and Enshrouded. Whether you're an experienced player or just starting your journey, there's a place for you here.</p>
        <p>Join our servers, participate in community events, and meet like-minded gamers. Our goal is to create an inclusive and respectful space where we can build, explore, and have fun together. Welcome aboard!</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="servers" class="servers-section">
      <div class="side-title">Servers</div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h2>Our Servers</h2>
        <p>Join us on our Minecraft and Enshrouded servers for countless adventures and a top-tier gaming experience.</p>
        <p>Our servers are well-maintained, ensuring smooth gameplay for everyone. Our moderators and administrators are always available to assist and ensure a positive experience for all players.</p>
        <div class="server-list">
          <article class="server">
            <div class="server-logo minecraft-logo"></div>
            <p>Join our Minecraft server for community-driven gameplay and events. Participate in building projects, survival challenges, and mini-games. We're currently in our fifth season, titled "Campus Block Party," offering new opportunities to create and explore together.</p>
            <div class="sub-section-container">
              <div class="sub-section server-info">
                <h4>Server Info</h4>
                  <div class="img"></div>
                  <code>play.thecubecollective.net</code>
                  <button onclick="copyButton()">
                    COPY URL ⧉
                  </button>
              </div>
              <div class="sub-section live-map">
                <h4>Maps</h4>
                  <div class="img"></div>
                  <code>thecubecollective.net/map</code>
                  <div class="button-holder">
                    <button class="map" onclick="window.location.href='http://play.thecubecollective.net:6707/'">
                      LIVE MAP <span class="live">●</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="seed"
                      onclick="window.open('https://www.chunkbase.com/apps/seed-map#seed=1757404403610633549&platform=java_1_21&dimension=overworld')">
                      SEED MAP
                    </button>
              </div>
              </div>
              <div class="sub-section status">
                <h4>Status</h4>
                  <table class="server-table">
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Status</td>
                      <td class="value <%= mcData.online ? 'status-online' : 'status-offline' %>">
                        <%= mcData.online ? 'Online' : 'Offline' %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Host</td>
                      <td class="value"><%= mcData.host %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Port</td>
                      <td class="value"><%= mcData.port %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Icon</td>
                      <td class="value"><img src="<%= mcData.icon %>" alt="Server Icon" class="icon"></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">MOTD</td>
                      <td class="value motd"><%- mcData.motd.html.replace(/\n/g, "<br>") %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Version</td>
                      <td class="value"><%= mcData.version.name_clean %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="label">Online Players</td>
                      <td class="value"><%= mcData.players.online %> / <%= mcData.players.max %></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="server">
            <div class="server-logo enshrouded-logo"></div>
            <p>Get ready for the Enshrouded server! Work together with other players to uncover hidden treasures, complete quests, and build a thriving community. The Enshrouded server offers a unique and immersive adventure.</p>
            <div class="sub-section-container">
              <div class="sub-section enshrouded-info">
                <h4>Exciting News!</h4>
                <p>Our Enshrouded server is launching soon and is currently undergoing testing. Stay tuned for an epic adventure filled with challenges and fun!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="discord" class="discord-section">
      <div class="side-title">Discord</div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h2>Join Our Discord</h2>
        <p>Stay connected with our community on Discord! Join discussions, participate in events, and get the latest updates.</p>
        <p>Our Discord server is the central hub for our community—chat with other members, receive important announcements, and join voice channels for in-game coordination.</p>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/qgnbRemYPz" target="_blank" class="discord-link">Join Our Discord Server</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about-section">
      <div class="side-title">About</div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>TheCubeCollective is a passionate gaming community that brings people together to enjoy Minecraft and Enshrouded. Founded by gamers for gamers, we focus on providing a welcoming and inclusive environment for players of all skill levels.</p>
        <p>We believe in the power of community and the joy of shared experiences. Whether you're here to compete, collaborate, or just have fun, you'll find a place at TheCubeCollective.</p>
        <div class="memberlist">
          <div class="player">
            <img src="https://mc-heads.net/body/Violetborne" alt="Violetborne's Head">
            <p class="op">Violetborne</p>
          </div>
          <div class="player">
